Race.SpecificTitle: Sixth Ward Fire Protection District -- 15 Mills Renewal - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Sixth Ward Fire Protection District Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Sixth Ward Fire Protection District of St. Helena Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), be authorized to continue to levy a special tax of fifteen (15) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $39,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year) for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and operating fire protection facilities and equipment for the District and paying the cost of obtaining water for fire protection?
